OL,3,CAuditor to take on three-stage charity
OL,4,C'Pain-a-thon'
OL,6,FITV News' Paul Crone spoke to Nigel as
OL,7,Fhe trained for his Painathon.
OL,9,FAn auditor known for pushing his body
OL,10,Fto the limit in unique ways for
OL,11,Fcharity is getting ready for his next
OL,12,Fgruelling challenge.
OL,14,FNigel Brookwell, from Wigan, is
OL,15,Fcurrently preparing for a "Painathon"
OL,16,Fwhich will see him pull a barge for
OL,17,Ftwo miles, walk barefoot for a futher
OL,18,Ftwo miles while carrying 35kg weights,
OL,19,Fand then finish the six mile trek on
OL,20,Fhis hands and knees.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
