FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1772644277
OL,3,CAuditor to take on three-stage charity
OL,4,C'Pain-a-thon'
OL,6,FHe's currently training for all three
OL,7,Fstretches, but says the final stretch
OL,8,Fon his hands and knees will be the
OL,9,Fhardest.
OL,11,FHe said: "It's so difficult to do. The
OL,12,Fbiggest enemy is cramp so you've got
OL,13,Fto keep yourself hydrated throughout.
OL,14,FOften my neck goes and I'm recognising
OL,15,Feverybody by their shoes... including
OL,16,Fmy mother."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
