OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1772644277
OL,3,CAuditor to take on three-stage charity
OL,4,C'Pain-a-thon'
OL,6,FThe 52-year-old father is hoping the
OL,7,Ftrek, which will begin at Wigan Pier
OL,8,Fand end at The Boars Head in Standish,
OL,9,Fwill raise #10,000 for local charity
OL,10,FDaffodil Dreams.
OL,12,FThe Wigan-based charity provides
OL,13,Fsupport to vulnerable families and
OL,14,Fchildren "no matter their background
OL,15,For their parents financial situation".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1772644277
OL,3,CAuditor to take on three-stage charity
OL,4,C'Pain-a-thon'
OL,6,FNigel said: "I had a great upbringing.
OL,7,FI've never gone hungry and I've had
OL,8,Fstability and love all my life. So to
OL,9,Fthink that some children don't get
OL,10,Fthat bothers me, and doesn't sit right
OL,11,Fwith me. So that motivates me to help
OL,12,Fthem."
OL,14,FThis is only the latest gruelling
OL,15,Fchallenge Nigel has taken on. In the
OL,16,Fpast, he has walked from Wigan to
OL,17,FStandish in a deep-sea diving suit,
OL,18,Fspent eight-and-a-half hours crawling
OL,19,Fon his hands and knees, and spent the
OL,20,Fnight blindfolded outside a church.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
