PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1772644277
OL,3,CAuditor to take on three-stage charity
OL,4,C'Pain-a-thon'
OL,6,FAll of his challenges have been done
OL,7,Fto support local charities and
OL,8,Forganisations.
OL,10,FHe said: "I'm very targeted in the
OL,11,Forganisations I help. I'm a very proud
OL,12,FWiganer and I want to help my own
OL,13,Ftown."
OL,15,FNigel's fundraiser can be found here.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
